Without steps to monitor and
check the spread of

22
00:09:21,810 --> 00:10:02,770
the disease, the plague is

23
00:10:02,770 --> 00:12:30,260
a danger

24
00:12:30,260 --> 00:12:41,990
to

25
00:12:41,990 --> 00:12:47,630
public health that can quickly get out of
hand. But the government has adopted a national

26
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:50,310
strategy to fight the disease.

27
00:12:50,310 --> 00:12:55,380
They now keep national statistics for every
case of the plague recorded in Madagascar

28
00:12:55,380 --> 00:13:01,370
which is then passed on to the World Health
Organization and with ICRC support, the

29
00:13:01,370 --> 00:13:20,680
prevention campaign in prison goes on.

30
00:13:20,680 --> 00:13:22,680
The challenge of this campaign is not to stop
in one single prison in the capital,

31
00:13:22,680 --> 00:13:24,680
but to develop these preventive measures
across Madagascar.

32
00:13:24,680 --> 00:13:26,680
and to get the entire prison system signed up
to this campaign, run by the authorities.

